      "name": "Texas Star \u00b7 5 Plates",
      "description": "Reactive five-arm star rig \u2014 central hub with five 8-inch round steel plates on radial arms 120 degrees apart in azimuth (5-pointed star geometry). Knocking a plate off shifts the star's balance and the remaining plates accelerate; classic action-pistol challenge.",
